TITLE: Manual Sign-In Redirection with clerkMiddleware
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to manually redirect unauthenticated users to the sign-in page using the redirectToSignIn helper with clerkMiddleware, offering more fine-grained control over the redirection flow.
SOURCE: https://github.com/clerk/javascript/blob/main/packages/nextjs/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-22_snippet_63

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { clerkMiddleware } from '@clerk/nextjs/server';

export default clerkMiddleware(auth => {
  // If you want more fine-grained control, you can always use the low-level redirectToSignIn helper
  if (!auth().userId) {
    return auth().redirectToSignIn();
  }

  return NextResponse.next();
});
```

