TITLE: Uploading Artifacts for Temporary Sites on Failure - GitHub Actions YAML
DESCRIPTION: Defines a GitHub Actions step to upload app artifacts (such as a temporary test site) following CI cancellation or failure. Uses the 'actions/upload-artifact@v4' action and relies on matrix variables for file naming. Requires that the 'long-running' app ID is substituted correctly in the path. Intended for extra debugging info after integration tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/clerk/javascript/blob/main/integration/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
